(44, 9, 14, 46, 1, 2, 2, 'call on thy name', 'Calling on the Name', 'This connection highlights the theme of calling on the name of Jesus Christ. Both passages emphasize the significance of those who invoke His name, linking the authority to bind believers in Acts with the sanctification of those who call upon Him in Corinthians.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
