(44, 9, 15, 44, 26, 17, 20, 'a chosen vessel unto me, to bear my name before the Gentiles', 'Connection of Paul''s Mission', 'Both passages emphasize Paul''s role as a chosen vessel to bear God''s name before the Gentiles. They highlight his mission to open their eyes and lead them to repentance and faith in God.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
