(44, 9, 23, 52, 2, 15, 16, 'the Jews took counsel to kill him', 'Persecution of Believers', 'This connection highlights the theme of persecution faced by early Christians. Both passages emphasize the hostility from the Jews towards those spreading the Gospel, culminating in violence against them.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
